` pipeline (design=`~treatment`, TMM + voom + eBayes) and write:\n  - `output/dea_results.csv` with columns `feature, logFC, AveExpr, t, P.Value,\n    adj.P.Val, B, group` (fwrite).\n  - `output/lmfit.rds` (fitted limma `lmFit` object, via `saveRDS`).\n  - `output/model_matrix.csv` (fwrite with row.names=TRUE).\nDo not persist any image output.\n\n## Deliverables\n\n- At least `output/dea_results.csv` must exist when you submit.\n- Full output set expected: dea_results.csv, model_matrix.csv under `output/`.\n\nWhen the deliverables are in `output/`, call `submit_done(success=true)` with a short\nsummary of how you solved it.\n\n## Workspace (read-only summary)\n```json\n{\n  \"OBJECTIVE.md\": {\n    \"_file\": \"OBJECTIVE.md\"\n  },\n  \"input\": {\n    \"counts.tsv\": {\n      \"_file\": \"counts.tsv\"\n    },\n    \"metadata.tsv\": {\n      \"_file\": \"metadata.tsv\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"meta.json\": {\n    \"_file\": \"meta.json\"\n  },\n  \"output\": {}\n}\n```\n\nSuccess hint: when `output/dea_results.csv` exists under the workspace, you may call submit_done(success=true).\n"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_oNI54NYwmgNXAYCTuVuB2hwc", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"plan\": \"1. Load the necessary libraries for differential expression analysis using limma.\\n2. Read the input data files: `counts.tsv` for gene expression data and `metadata.tsv` for sample metadata.\\n3. Prepare the design matrix using the formula `~treatment`.\\n4. Normalize the data using TMM normalization with `edgeR::calcNormFactors`.\\n5. Apply the `voom` transformation to model the mean-variance relationship.\\n6. Fit the linear model using `lmFit` and apply empirical Bayes moderation with `eBayes`.\\n7. Extract the differential expression results using `topTable`.\\n8. Save the results to `output/dea_results.csv`.\\n9. Save the fitted model object to `output/lmfit.rds`.\\n10. Save the design matrix to `output/model_matrix.csv`.\\n11. Verify the existence of `output/dea_results.csv` and submit the task as done.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (801 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_oNI54NYwmgNXAYCTuVuB2hwc"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_GR1XYVmhB4cY9nvDwDT5MwX0", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"relative_path\": \"input/counts.tsv\"}", "name": "read_text_file"}}, {"id": "call_yR0e5AcSbVHj3bnh9dx5x8mh", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"relative_path\": \"input/metadata.tsv\"}", "name": "read_text_file"}}]}], "hide_old_env_states": false, "hide_old_action_content": false}, "next_agent_state": {"tools": [{"type": "function", "info": {"name": "run_shell", "description": "Run a shell command in the task work_dir (bash -lc).", "parameters": {"type": "object", "properties": {"command": {"description": "Shell command string passed to `bash -lc`.", "title": "Command", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["command"]}}}, {"type": "function", "info": {"name": "read_text_file", "description": "Read a UTF-8 text file relative to work_dir.", "parameters": {"type": "object", "properties": {"relative_path": {"description": "Path under the workspace (not absolute).", "title": "Relative Path", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["relative_path"]}}}, {"type": "function", "info": {"name": "write_text_file", "description": "Write text to a path under work_dir (creates parent dirs).", "parameters": {"type": "object", "properties": {"relative_path": {"description": "Path under the workspace (not absolute).", "title": "Relative Path", "type": "string"}, "content": {"description": "Full file body to write as UTF-8 text.", "title": "Content", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["relative_path", "content"]}}}, {"type": "function", "info": {"name": "run_rscript", "description": "Run inline R code via Rscript -e (single line safe for agents).", "parameter